data.app-config.production.yaml:
app:
  baseUrl: https://83.32.50.24:8082

integrations:
  github:
    - host: github.com
      token: ${GITHUB_TOKEN}
  gitlab:
    - host: gitlab.com
      token: "not-used" # Esto evita el error ForwardedError de tus logs

backend:
  baseUrl: https://83.32.50.24:8082
  listen:
    port: 7007
    host: 0.0.0.0
  auth:
    keys:
      - secret: "secret"
  csp:
    upgradeInsecureRequests: false
  cors:
    origin: https://83.32.50.24:8082
    methods: [GET, HEAD, PATCH, POST, PUT, DELETE]
    credentials: true
  database:
    client: pg
    connection:
      host: ${POSTGRES_HOST}
      port: ${POSTGRES_PORT}
      user: ${POSTGRES_USER}
      password: ${POSTGRES_PASSWORD}

auth:
  environment: production
  providers:
    guest:
      dangerouslyAllowOutsideDevelopment: true
    github:
      production:
        clientId: ${AUTH_GITHUB_CLIENT_ID}
        clientSecret: ${AUTH_GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET}
      development:
        clientId: ${AUTH_GITHUB_CLIENT_ID}
        clientSecret: ${AUTH_GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET}

# Configuraci칩n para TechDocs y Cat치logo (necesaria para que no falle al iniciar)
catalog:
  import:
    entityFilename: catalog-info.yaml
  locations: []

techdocs:
  builder: 'local'
  generator:
    runIn: 'docker'
  publisher:
    type: 'local'
